CINCINNATI BAR ASSN.
v.
MOORE 2018-1758 Supreme Court of Ohio. August 8, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

DISCIPLINARY CASE

Sua sponte, Rodger William Moore, Attorney Registration No. 0074144, last known business address in Alexandria, Kentucky, found in contempt for failure to surrender his certificate of admission and failure to file an affidavit of compliance on or before July 1, 2019.
